    <text id="A9810T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>John Janney resigns from a government post in a letter addressed to the Speaker
                    of the House of Delegates (John B. Baldwin).</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <opener>
                    
                    <salute>To the Speaker of the House of Delegates of
                    Virginia:--<lb/>Sir:</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I hereby resign into the hands of the General Assembly of Virginia the Office of
                    Commissioner to West Virginia. The condition of my eyesight renders it
                    impossible for me to perform the duties, and not being aware of any other
                    authority to fill a vaccancy in the recess, I make this communication now that
                    you may, before the adjournment, take such action as may be proper.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Very Respectfully Your <abbr expan="Obedient">Obt.</abbr> Servant,</salute>
                    <signed>John Janney</signed>
                    <seg type="postscript">
                        <name type="recipient">John B Baldwin Esq Speaker</name>
                    </seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
